title: 0.13 dev
body:
This pull request has multiple changes on weex-vue-render, including performance optimization and  bugfixes.

* release weex-vue-render v0.11.41 on npm.
* fix scoped style calculation and analysis.
* should use `$processStyle` on vue-loader config.
* slider-neighbor support `current-item-scale`.
* fix image loading during `animation.transition`.
* support updating slider's `index` in runtime.
* other bugfixes.

title: * [android] Fix mixing background-color and border-color(rgba)
